Current Job Openings


					To apply for jobs with AEP, please register to create an online profile and apply online. By registering, you can:
				

Receive e-mailed alerts when jobs that interest you become available
Apply for jobs and submit your resume.


					To apply for jobs with AEP’s affiliate based in Chicago, Ill., AEP Energy, view jobs and apply online on their site.
Please Note:

We do not accept e-mailed resumes. We only consider resumes submitted as part of the online application process.
We do not respond to general e-mails about openings. We provide all openings online and offer search tools to help
						you find the right job.

