Great Lakes Power Transmission Equipment Sales, Service


































Sales & 24/7 Service: 800-325-6880
sales@glpower.com
Surplus Inventory Sale






















Sales, Service and OEM Remanufacturing of Powershift Transmissions, Power Take Offs, Fluid Couplings, Torque Converters, Gear Boxes, Axles and Drive Train Components and Power Transmission Equipment
Great Lakes Power Products is a full-line distributor, manufacturer and rebuilder of power transmission products and accessories. The company is an authorized distributor and service center for Twin Disc, Dana Spicer, Funk Manufacturing, Wichita Clutch and other leading off-highway power transmission equipment manufacturers.
Our 14 locations, staffed by an experienced team of factory-authorized technicians, serve customers worldwide. If your application involves off highway, marine, agricultural, oil and gas or industrial power transmission products, service or reman, we're the people to call.

Our Locations


