Career Opportunities





















Late Breaking News


Paul Greely Celebrates 40th Year with Great Lakes Power
At their annual branch management retreat in Orlando, Florida, President Rick Pennza and Vice Presidents Dave Allen and Stephen Allen presented to Paul Greely his 40th anniversary award.
For 40 of Great Lakes Power's 44 year history, Paul has worked his way up through the organization from his early days as a service technician fast forward now to managing the company's Cincinnati, Ohio and Statesville, North Carolina branch operations.
"The company has been blessed with so many long-term hard working dedicated employees over the years," commented Rick Pennza. "Paul is one of those highly regarded talents that have contributed to the success of our organization these many years."
Congratulations Paul on reaching this valued milestone.
Kurt Ferneding, head of Cincinnati's service operation, (on the right), congratulates Paul Greely (left)

Great Lakes Power Products management congratulates Paul Greely. From left to right, Stephen Allen, VP/Regional Sales Manager, Paul Greely, Rick Pennza, President, David Allen, VP of Service Operations



 






