Power 
		

Products 
		













Nearly 70 Years 
		

in the making 
		













Quality Tools 
		

& Equipment 
		








 












&nbsp br>
		
 








Delivering extreme value for suppliers and consumers, our durable, high quality woodworking & metalworking machinery is engineered to outperform the competition. In our never-ending quest for superior service and continuous improvement, we welcome your feedback and know you will appreciate the reliability of our products and support resources.

















NEW PRODUCTS
Innovation is a continuous process at General International. Please take a few moments to browse our complete list of soon-to-arrive and new product solutions.







GLOBAL CONNECTION
With our international expansion, we established lasting relationships in over 15 countries during the past 70 years. Our U.S. headquarters is constantly working with industry-leading global partners to develop the next generation of woodworking and metalworking machinery.







VIDEO TUTORIALS
Coming soon! We can’t wait to show you our video tutorials for your tools. Easy to access video tutorials will help you find the information you need about your tools and machinery.







ADAPTABILITY
During the past 70 years, users and distributors alike have learned to trust General International product solutions. By listening to our customers, we have been able to respond to constantly-changing requirements and market dynamics.












                Unmatched Quality 
            



Machinery and Tools People Trust

 




CORPORATE PROMISE
We offer a 100% satisfaction guarantee on our product. Our industry-leading 2 year limited warranty is a reflection of the quality level of General products, and our commitment to delivering exceptional support and service.


NEWEST TECHNOLOGY
Our research initiatives insure the latest, most technologically advanced solutions and safety-conscious designs are available to General International customers.   Our new online product support tools include parts & troubleshooting information plus a service representative contact portal.  These online tools insure fingertip access to parts breakdowns and troubleshooting information 24 x 7.








HIGH PERFORMANCE
During the past 70 years, General International has consistently produced the highest quality, superior value, woodworking and metalworking machinery.   We have an extensive engineering, manufacturing, quality, and distribution knowledge base within our 10,000 current employees who are committed to providing the most durable, high performance powered equipment on earth.


SAFTEY STANDARDS
All General International products are engineered, designed, tested and certified with your safety in mind.   Our manufacturing processes and supply chain partners ensure the highest product safety levels standards are met.











