                QUALITY SINCE 1946
            



Customer Oriented. Mechanically Driven.

 
Established 1946Dedicated to a product line of woodworking tools. Original headquarters based in Montreal, CA.
Sparks Start to Fly in 2001Metalworking machinery emerged, and we began offering these products to small and medium sized machine shops.
USA Headquarter Established in 2014Proud to announce new USA headquarters, established in Whitehouse, Ohio.







                FOR THE MODERN AGE
            









Communication and distribution are key strategies, and our advancing technology will easily help guide our suppliers and consumers in the right direction. 













INFORMATION AND SPECS
Accurate up-to-date specifications for all our tools and machinery in the support section on our webpage.


RESPONSIVE DESIGN
Our site will adapt to any mobile device you’re using to keep our information readable and user friendly.


HELP & TUTORIALS
You will find the best resources for your tools with our online support videos, help, and tutorials.
















ONLINE CATALOG
